<p>The Textbook of Microbiology by C.P. Baveja is a comprehensive and widely-used textbook that covers the fundamental principles of microbiology. It is available in PDF format, making it accessible to students and researchers worldwide. The textbook provides a detailed overview of microbial diversity, microbial structure and function, microbial genetics, and microbial ecology.</p>
